(4, 'about us', '<p>Choosing the right company to handle your travel arrangements in Europe is most important, we are an experienced tour operators in Europe based in India. &nbsp;We arrange all types of tours in Europe especially in Italy. Our list includes Hill stations. Forests. Mountains. Rivers. Bird sanctuaries. Back waters beaches pilgrim destinations. Adventurous .Cultural. Honey moon. &nbsp;<strong>Mini van packages(Maximum 8 passengers),</strong> weekend trips, group tours, Business trips Etc&hellip;</p>\n<p>We provide all possible help and guidelines to make your tour enjoyable and risk free we can organize tours anywhere in Europe within your budget</p>\n<p>We have our group of persons located in all over the Europe, &nbsp;Italy Germany Switzerland Austria Engaland. Hungary Rumania Turkey France Spain Portugal Netherland Belgium Poland etc.. We provide a wide range of Europe tour packages at affordable rates</p>\n<p>Our aim is to get 100% customer satisfaction and for this we select the best quality hotels and who have good service records. We have all types of taxicars mini van&rsquo;s tourist buses and private vehicles. All our drivers are well mannered and know multiple languages.</p>\n<p>We understand that while you wish to be alone, you do not want to feel isolated. Which is why, the moment you land in airport &nbsp;we hand over you a mobile phone, yours for the length of your stay. The phone will have all the emergency numbers fed in, including those of your tour planer in your own country and senior Vacanza mondiale staff in Europe. We are quite sure you will never need to use the phone. But if you do, call us any time of the day or night. You&rsquo;ll always find a friend at the other end.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '5317794363fa41907560_663507280361587_1493182182_n.jpg', '2015-02-06 10:46:01');
