(126, 31, 'Day 2 ', '<p>Continental Breakfast at the Hotel Transfer to Avila English Speaking Guide for Avila City tour Visit Avila Basilica &nbsp;Lunch On the way to Fatima &nbsp;Arrive Fatima &nbsp;Evening free for Religious Activit Dinner at&nbsp;Hotel Over Night at Fatima &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '53d36c61dab8bFatima.jpg'),
